Subject: Re: [VB] stuck drum again

Yes, this is how I do it too. Make sure the tongues of the shoes are
seated in the slots of the cylinder ends. Then fold the rubber seal
forward and around the cylinder body, making sure that they fit and seal,
all the way around as well.

Good call Clara! It's the kind of detail that I just take for granted.

cal

